<?xml version="1.0" encoding="GB2312"?>
    <?xml:stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="/xsl/xsl_c/methodmanual.xsl"?><manpage>
<volume>图形系统</volume>
<method>CImage::New </method>
    <description>
        <para>
            创建图片对象。
        </para>
    </description>    	
    <syntax>
        <return_val> ECode </return_val>
        <parameters>
            <api_param>
                <param_inout>[in]</param_inout>
                <param_type> IInputStream* </param_type>
                <param_name> stream </param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>
指向<link url="../../../../StreamIO/interface_i_input_stream.html">           IInputStream             </link>接口指针，用于从二进制流中读取输入字节                    </para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>
            <api_param>
                <param_inout>[in]</param_inout>
                <param_type> ImageFormat </param_type>
                <param_name> format </param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>
图片格式， <link url="../../datatype/ImageFormat.htm"> ImageFormat</link> 枚举数据类型 </para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>
            <api_param>
                <param_inout>[out]</param_inout>
                <param_type> IImage** </param_type>
                <param_name> image </param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>
指向图片对象的 <link url="../IImage.htm">IImage</link>接口指针的指针，用于获取图片对象IImage接口指针 </para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>
        </parameters>
    </syntax>

<return>
    <para>
            如果方法调用成功，则返回NOERROR；如果stream为NULL或者读取的二进制数据流大小无效，则方法调用失败，并返回E_INVALID_ARGUMENT。    </para>
    <para>
    	      更多返回值信息，参见 <link url="../../../../../../car_technology/fundamental/development_environment/car/ECode.htm">ECode</link>相关帮助。</para>
</return>
    <requirements>
                <system>
            <system_name>
Elastos操作系统           </system_name>
        </system>
        <headerfile>
            <file_name>ElGrafix.h</file_name>
        </headerfile>
        <library>
            <lib_name>elastos.lib</lib_name>
        </library>
    </requirements>
<remarks>
	      <para>
             该方法是用已有的图片来创建图片对象;   
        </para>      
        <para>
             举例声明一个图片：    ec = CImage::New(stream, ImageFormat_Jpg, &amp;m_pImage);   
        </para>
</remarks>
</manpage>